definitions.definition: The wife of Tyndareus and mother of Helen , Clytemnestra and Castor and Pollux hatched from eggs as a result of a seduction by Zeus in the guise of a swan
38 Leda , a main belt asteroid ; not to be confused with the Jovian moon.
